@* Program Impact *@
<div class="content-section impact-section">
    <div class="impact-content">
        <h2>Building California's Teacher Workforce</h2>
        <p class="impact-text">
            The Student Teacher Stipend Program addresses a critical barrier in teacher preparation by providing
            financial support during the intensive student teaching period. By removing financial obstacles,
            California is investing in a diverse and well-prepared teaching workforce to serve all students.
        </p>
        <div class="impact-stats">
            <div class="impact-stat">
                <div class="stat-number">30,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Potential Stipends Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-stat">
                <div class="stat-number">$10,000</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Support Per Candidate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-stat">
